SUMMARY:
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=1 -->
 The Nuclear Regulatory Commission (NRC) is publishing for public comment a notice of receipt of a petition for rulemaking
dated February 10, 1994, which was filed with the Commission by Ohio Citizens for Responsible Energy, Inc. (OCRE).
The petition was docketed by the NRC on February 15, 1994, and has been assigned Docket No. PRM&hyph;9&hyph;2. OCRE
