SUMMARY:
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=1 -->
 On November 13, 1992, the West Virginia Department of Commerce, Labor &amp; Environmental Resources; Division of
Environmental Protection; Office of Air Quality (WVOAQ) submitted a request to EPA to redesignate the Charleston
moderate ozone nonattainment area (Kanawha and Putnam Counties) from nonattainment to attainment. On November
