<!-- PJG STAG 4702 -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=80 g=1 f=1 -->
&sect;280.230 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=89 g=1 f=1 -->
Operating an underground storage tank or underground storage tank system. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
(a) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Operating an UST or UST system prior to foreclosure. 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
A holder, prior to foreclosure or its equivalents, is not an ``operator'' of a petroleum UST or UST system for purposes
of compliance with the corrective action requirements of &sect;&sect;280.51 through 280.67 and the UST technical
standards, provided the holder is not in control of or does not have responsibility for the daily operation of the UST
or UST system. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(b) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Operating an UST or UST system after foreclosure. 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(1) A holder who has not participated in management prior to foreclosure and who acquires a petroleum UST or UST system
through foreclosure or its equivalents is not an ``operator'' of the UST or UST system for purposes of compliance with
the corrective action requirements under &sect;&sect;280.51 through 280.67, provided that the holder within 15
days following foreclosure or its equivalents, empties all of its USTs and UST systems so that no more than 2.5 centimeters
(one inch) of residue, or 0.3 percent by weight of the total capacity of the UST system, remains in the system; leaves
vent lines open and functioning; and caps and secures all other lines, pumps, manways, and ancillary equipment. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) In addition, the holder must either: 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(i) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Permanently close the UST or UST system 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
in accordance with &sect;&sect;280.71 through 280.74, except &sect;280.72(b); or 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(ii) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Temporarily close the UST or UST system 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
